#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn43.44"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn43.44:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 43 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 43 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.44:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn43.44:0.3"
msgid "44. Parāyanasutta "
msgstr "44. The Haven "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.373, sc1
#. VAR: Parāyanañca → parāyaṇañca (bj)
msgctxt "sn43.44:1.1"
msgid "“Parāyanañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi parāyanagāmiñca maggaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you the haven and the path that leads to the haven. "

msgctxt "sn43.44:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha. "
msgstr "Listen … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.44:1.3"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, parāyanaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is the haven? "

msgctxt "sn43.44:1.4"
msgid "Yo, bhikkhave, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—"
msgstr "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion. "

msgctxt "sn43.44:1.5"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, parāyanaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called the haven. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.44:1.6"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, parāyanagāmī maggo? "
msgstr "And what is the path that leads to the haven? "

msgctxt "sn43.44:1.7"
msgid "Kāyagatāsati. "
msgstr "Mindfulness of the body. "

msgctxt "sn43.44:1.8"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, parāyanagāmimaggo. "
msgstr "This is called the path that leads to the haven. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.44:1.9"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, desitaṃ vo mayā parāyanaṃ, desito parāyanagāmimaggo. "
msgstr "So, mendicants, I’ve taught you the haven and the path that leads to the haven. "

msgctxt "sn43.44:1.10"
msgid "Yaṃ, bhikkhave, satthārā karaṇīyaṃ sāvakānaṃ hitesinā anukampakena anukampaṃ upādāya, kataṃ vo taṃ mayā. "
msgstr "Out of compassion, I’ve done what a teacher should do who wants what’s best for their disciples. "

msgctxt "sn43.44:1.11"
msgid "Etāni, bhikkhave, rukkhamūlāni, etāni suññāgārāni. Jhāyatha, bhikkhave, mā pamādattha; mā pacchā vippaṭisārino ahuvattha. Ayaṃ vo amhākaṃ anusāsanī”ti. "
msgstr "Here are these roots of trees, and here are these empty huts. Practice absorption, mendicants! Don’t be negligent! Don’t regret it later! This is my instruction to you.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn43.44:1.12"
msgid "(Yathā asaṅkhataṃ tathā vitthāretabbaṃ.) (33) "
msgstr "(This should be expanded as with the unconditioned.) "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn43.44:1.13"
msgid "Tettiṃsatimaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn43.44:1.14"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn43.44:2.1"
msgid "Asaṅkhataṃ anataṃ anāsavaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:2.2"
msgid "Saccañca pāraṃ nipuṇaṃ sududdasaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:2.3"
msgid "Ajajjaraṃ dhuvaṃ apalokitaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:2.4"
msgid "Anidassanaṃ nippapañca santaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn43.44:3.1"
msgid "Amataṃ paṇītañca sivañca khemaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:3.2"
msgid "Taṇhākkhayo acchariyañca abbhutaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:3.3"
msgid "Anītikaṃ anītikadhammaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:3.4"
msgid "Nibbānametaṃ sugatena desitaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn43.44:4.1"
msgid "Abyābajjho virāgo ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:4.2"
msgid "suddhi mutti anālayo; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:4.3"
msgid "Dīpo leṇañca tāṇañca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn43.44:4.4"
msgid "saraṇañca parāyananti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn43.44:4.5"
msgid "Asaṅkhatasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ. "
msgstr "The Linked Discourses on the unconditioned are complete."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
